#### PENTACLES

#### Six

<span id="img_pe06"></span> <span align="CENTER"> [![](tn/pe06.jpg)  
Click to enlarge](img/pe06.jpg.md)</span>

A person in the guise of a merchant weighs money in a pair of scales and
distributes it to the needy and distressed. It is a testimony to his own
success in life, as well as to his goodness of heart. *Divinatory
Meanings*: Presents, gifts, gratification another account says
attention, vigilance now is the accepted time, present prosperity, etc.
*Reversed*: Desire, cupidity, envy, jealousy, illusion.

